---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import QuickContact from '../components/QuickContact.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - The Tower Security Agency">
	<Navigation />

	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Us</h1>
			<p>Leading Security Solutions with Military Excellence</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="about-intro">
				<div class="intro-image">
					<img src="/compressed_1mb.jpg" alt="Security Team">
				</div>
				<div class="intro-text">
					<h2>Welcome to The Tower Security Agency</h2>
					<p>We are one of the leading security organizations with determination to cater to the Security, Safety, Preventive Services and Surveillance needs of your organizations.</p>
					<p>Our Security force consists of well trained and experienced personnel recruited from Ex-Servicemen, Paramilitary services companies of well repute and trained civilians or reasonably qualified with relevant experience in the field.</p>
					<p>Organizations requiring security staff with computer knowledge to handle daily documentation and records work can benefit from our specially trained personnel who are deployed to suit your specific needs.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" style="background: var(--light);">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-title">
				<h2>Company Profile</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="profile-content">
				<div class="profile-text">
					<p>The Tower Security Agency is headed by a class Ex-service gentleman as its Managing Director, <strong>Mr. R.D. Moorthy</strong>, and assisted by highly qualified professionals from various walks, specialized in strong security, safety and technical background such as Human Resources Development, Fire and Safety, Surveillance, Public Relations, First Aid and allied services in the clients premises.</p>
					<p>We perceive the requirements of our clients are <strong>TOTAL and LONG TERM</strong>, and to achieve the same we implement stringent deploying techniques by our reliable and efficient personnel, who are smartly uniformed and equipped.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="profile-image">
					<img src="/ArmedGard.png" alt="Professional Security">
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="vmv-grid">
				<div class="vmv-card card">
					<div class="vmv-icon">🎯</div>
					<h3>Our Vision</h3>
					<p>Our Vision is to mark a unique position in industry by providing quality services and satisfy client's needs. Also to bring advanced technology in place to provide best in class service.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="vmv-card card">
					<div class="vmv-icon">🚀</div>
					<h3>Our Mission</h3>
					<p>To be a leader in providing protection, security and investigation service. To deliver high quality security solutions at a competitive rate.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="vmv-card card">
					<div class="vmv-icon">💡</div>
					<h3>Our Objective</h3>
					<p>We believe in providing your industry/organization the maximum security protection with a minimum budgetary impact tailor-made to the individual and specific needs of the client.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" style="background: var(--primary); color: var(--white);">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-title">
				<h2 style="color: var(--white);">Our Approach</h2>
				<p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Excellence through disciplined execution</p>
			</div>
			<div class="approach-grid">
				<div class="approach-item">
					<h4>Stringent Selection</h4>
					<p>Utmost attention is given to the suitability of our personnel in accordance with stringent parameters laid down in our policy. Age, Education, Physical Fitness and antecedent verification ensure only the best are selected.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="approach-item">
					<h4>Ex-Servicemen Priority</h4>
					<p>The security personnel proposed to be deployed are able-bodied individuals with ample education background. They are inducted through a system of screening and selection. Preference is given for Ex-Servicemen and the same can be sourced for your total requirement if the client so desires.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="approach-item">
					<h4>Professional Management</h4>
					<p>The promoters of the company consist of veterans of Defence forces, Police and Human Resources, with each one of them claiming their specialized skills in different areas thereby contributing to the strength of the organization.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="approach-item">
					<h4>Expert Guidance</h4>
					<p>Besides expertise from different fields have been drawn with sufficient seniority and prolonged experience who assist the company in formulation of policies and principles.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-title">
				<h2>Why Partner With Us</h2>
				<p>Commitment to excellence in every aspect</p>
			</div>
			<div class="benefits-grid">
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">01</div>
					<h3>Experienced Leadership</h3>
					<p>Led by ex-servicemen with decades of experience in security and defense operations.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">02</div>
					<h3>Trained Personnel</h3>
					<p>All security staff undergo rigorous training in security protocols, first aid, firefighting, and crisis management.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">03</div>
					<h3>Advanced Technology</h3>
					<p>Integration of modern surveillance systems and communication tools for enhanced security.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">04</div>
					<h3>Customized Solutions</h3>
					<p>Security plans tailored to your specific requirements and budget constraints.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">05</div>
					<h3>24/7 Monitoring</h3>
					<p>Round-the-clock supervision with patrolling supervisors equipped with communication tools.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-number">06</div>
					<h3>Proven Track Record</h3>
					<p>Serving 40+ satisfied clients across various industries with exceptional service.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<QuickContact />
	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
		color: var(--white);
		padding: 120px 0 80px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.page-hero h1 {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.page-hero p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.about-intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.intro-image img,
	.profile-image img {
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}

	.intro-text h2 {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
	}

	.intro-text p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.profile-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.profile-text p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.vmv-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
	}

	.vmv-card {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 40px 30px;
	}

	.vmv-icon {
		font-size: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
	}

	.vmv-card h3 {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.vmv-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.approach-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
	}

	.approach-item h4 {
		color: var(--gold);
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.approach-item p {
		color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.benefits-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
	}

	.benefit-card {
		padding: 30px;
		background: var(--white);
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
	}

	.benefit-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
	}

	.benefit-number {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--gold);
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		opacity: 0.3;
	}

	.benefit-card h3 {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.benefit-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-hero {
			padding: 100px 0 60px;
		}

		.page-hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
		}

		.page-hero p {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.about-intro,
		.profile-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 40px;
		}

		.profile-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.profile-image {
			order: -1;
		}

		.vmv-grid,
		.approach-grid,
		.benefits-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
